        <main>
          <section style="margin-bottom: 40px;">
            <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 16px;">What is Krater.ai?</h2>
            <p>Krater is the ultimate AI SuperApp that gives you access to over 350 AI models from leading providers like OpenAI, Anthropic, Google, Meta, and more. Generate images, videos, music, and chat with the most advanced AI models – all with one subscription starting at $7.50/month.</p>
          </section>
          
