              <li><a href="/models/deepseek-v3">DeepSeek V3</a> – Advanced reasoning model</li>
              <li><a href="/models/grok-3">Grok 3</a> – xAI's conversational model</li>
            </ul>
            <p><a href="/models">View all 350+ AI models →</a></p>
          </section>
          
          <section style="margin-bottom: 40px;">
            <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 16px;">Key Features</h2>
            <ul>
              <li>Chat with 350+ AI models from OpenAI, Anthropic, Google, Meta, and more</li>
              <li>Generate stunning images with FLUX, DALL-E, and Stable Diffusion</li>
              <li>Create videos with Runway, Kling, and other video AI models</li>
              <li>Compose music with Suno and Udio</li>
              <li>No API keys required – everything works out of the box</li>
            </ul>
          </section>
          
